ISCP Programming connector for PICs This 6 pin header contains all the lines necessary for programming most PIC microcontrollers. Here is the connector we sell at SparkFun:
  • Polarized Connectors - Header (6-Pin) (PRT-08094)
It is used on this SparkFun product:
  • SparkFun UDB5 - PIC UAV Development Board (DEV-11703)
Also, if you need a nice PIC programmer, please check these out:
  • MPLAB PICkit 3 (PGM-09973)
